README

Editing TEI with LibreOffice.
Source files are .fodt under fodt/


Use styles
---------
'Title' : for the document title || meta dc:title
'Author' : $META/office:meta/meta:initial-creator
'Language' : $META/office:meta/dc:language


Publishing to Apple IBooks
=======
Using itunes producer.
The epub filename must not contain underscores.
The cover image must be > 1400px smallest
dc:date from package.opf must be non empty.


Replace CR with line breaks:
find: </text:p>\s*\n\s*<text:p text:style-name="[\w\d]+">
replace with: <text:line-break/>\n


Surse carti frantuzesti:

- biblitoeca aia din Quebec, canadiana, avea multe carti in doc
- ebooks libres et gratuits
- book feed, aparuse ceva
- universitatea suisse cu Jean Calvin

Surse carti english:
- Gutenberg
- adelaide
